    <item>
      <title>飓风海伦导致对芯片制造和太阳能至关重要的石英矿停产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hurricane-halts-quartz-mines-vital-for-chipmaking-and-solar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受飓风海伦影响，北卡罗来纳州两家采矿企业停工近一周，这两家企业生产了全球四分之三以上的高纯度石英，而石英是太阳能和半导体行业的关键材料。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hurricane-halts-quartz-mines-vital-for-chipmaking-and-solar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 04:07:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
